92
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:55,240
Lu Zhao, I have to save him.

93
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,240
I'll go with you.

94
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:11,160
Xiao Ren, rescuing Song Lou...

95
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,600
