111
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,880
From now on,

112
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,840
Xuntian Sect will be entrusted to you.

113
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,080
Yes, I'll safeguard your badge...

114
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,400
